info.description: ## Snaky Android Test --- If you want to be able to try out the API using the **Execute** or **TRY** button from this page - an android device should be connected using `adb` - the server should have been started using `./culebratester2 start-server`  then you will be able to invoke the API and see the responses.   # noqa: E501
